Weapon and Armor Proficiency		KEY:Samurai ~ Weapon and Armor Proficiency		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Class Feature.Samurai Class Feature.SpecialQuality																																			DESC:Samurai are proficient with all simple and martial weapons and with light and medium armor. Samurai are not proficient with shields. Note that armor check penalties for armor heavier than leather apply to the skills Balance, Climb, Escape Artist, Hide, Jump, Move Silently, Pick Pocket, and Tumble. Also, Swim checks suffer a -1 penalty for every 5 pounds of armor and equipment carried.																																															ABILITY:Internal|AUTOMATIC|TYPE=ArmorProfMedium|TYPE=WeaponProfMartial																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																															SOURCEPAGE:p.31
